Analyze this image and output ONLY valid English JSON (100-128 tokens total) using this exact template and key order:

{"subject":"","action":"","details":"","scene":"","composition":"","camera":"","lighting":"","style":""}

Field definitions (use concise string fragments, NO full sentences):
- subject: main subject
- action: pose, state, or behavior
- details: clothing, textures, materials, props
- scene: environment, background, spatial context
- composition: framing, angle, shot type, placement
- camera: photo specs (e.g., 35mm, close-up, depth of field) or neutral plausible description
- lighting: source, direction, contrast, color temp
- style: visual style

Constraints:
- Describe ONLY clearly visible details. Do not repeat info across fields. No negative wording. 
- Strictly EXCLUDE hype/filler tags (e.g., masterpiece, best quality, 4k, 8k, UHD, trending on ArtStation). 
- No extra text or explanations outside the JSON.